BBQ Champ UK - Series 1, Episode 2




In the second episode of the series the seven remaining contestants must first take on the regally named King of the Kebab challenge. Then it's time for the contestants to get grab their buckets and spades and head to the south coast for their Seaside Sizzler location challenge where they'll be cooking for families on the beach.




Original Air Date: 07-Aug-2015
